PRO ContrastBox::CLEANUP

   @cat_pro_error_handler

   Obj_Destroy, self.contrastID
   Obj_Destroy, self.bufferID

   self -> MOVEABLEBOX::CLEANUP ; Don't forget this line or memory leakage WILL occur!!!

   self -> Report, /Completed

END


